             The Curse of the Sword of Sunnah
             ================================
   Legends speak of the great sword of Sunnah. It is said that
after a great battle with an enemy force, the great Sunnah was
defeated and his sword was stolen. It is said that the sword
possesses immense power and it would destroy anyone that tried
to wield it. One must be a ninja master in order to handle its
power and magic. The enemies who stole the sword knew that they
could not use it, so they destroyed it, preventing Sunnah from
using it. Its pieces have been scattered around and hidden
for centuries. As the legend goes, if anyone can bring the
three pieces of the sword together, it is possible to re-unite them.
   When the sword was destroyed, a dark curse of dishonor was placed
upon it. The only way to restore honor to the sword is to sacrifice
a piece of your own soul. You must find the pieces of the sword and
restore its honor.
This quest is for mid to high levels.
